reviews.text:
Woah, very impressive man. This is really good. I've actually been working on this profile myself and picked up CAP Gingerbread just a couple weeks back, so I gave it a mix. The cream filling is on point for sure. The gingerbread does a great job at bringing that soft cookie and ginger taste that the actually lil debbie's carry. The only thing it lacks is a bit of the oat flavor and texture, but that has been very difficult to come by in vape form. &#xD;
&#xD;
I've already mixed a couple bottles of this as is, I'll probably be trying out with a little RF oatmeal cookie and maybe a touch of FA almond to bring some texture out.
